item.description: Grab a pair of headphones, because this article has a soundtrack! Check out the first song in this Youtube playlist: does it remind you of anything? hint hint (image credit) If your formative years were later than 1990, your first thought was likely “Mario Kart”. You wouldn’t be alone - more and more people seem to be finding (and even writing!) music they can only describe as “Mario Kart Music”.
